rating_comment: It is a great place to stay and very secured. The host Mr. Saleh is very cooperative and helpful and also his other staff. Good place for family. It is also very neat and clean and properly maintained.

Rating, 5 stars,  · September 2017,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: This is my second time staying with Saleh and I have to say that he is a great host. With his many apartments around Dhaka, he is super helpful when things are needed. 2 things to notice: the area of this house is really quiet hence the gates close at 11-12 pm and will have to wake up the caretaker at night to open the main gate downstairs. Also the location on the map in Airbnb is a bit off I have mentioned this to the host, and in order to get an accurate idea of the location it’s best to check yourself in google. Overall a good stay with Saleh specially for the price.
